snippet.title: #tishatalks LIVE is back this Friday with Amber Griffiths!
snippet.description: It's back on at its brand new day and time, and with a special new guest to kick off 2022! Tune in LIVE or catch the replay this Friday at 10:45am MST as I welcome Ms. Amber Griffiths, Maker of Legends with Your Brand by Design, to the virtual studio Friday, January 7! We'll dive into "How to Claim Your Legendary Persona." Find it on LinkedIn, Facebook or on YouTube at http://bit.ly/tishaonyoutube See you there!
